Minecraft 1.21 Tutorial Playlist  http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEB388783144C45A8
Minecraft 1.21 introduced the Trial Spawner, we can use this block found inside the Trial Chamber strucutre to farm slimes! Slimes can spawn from Trial Spawners, this makes for an easy alternative to grindy slime farms.
